ght:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;常吃油炸食品皮肤会变差】“油炸能给我的不多，只有快乐。”可是：①即使是蔬菜，油炸后也会热量翻倍，常吃易胖；②油炸过程中会产生丙烯酰胺等有害健康的物质；③油炸食物还可能促进身体炎症反应，让皮肤变差。那有没有什么办法，能享受油炸快乐的同时，又减少对身体的伤害啊&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[抓狂]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_zhuakuang-c007ffb7fe.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（央视新闻）&lt;a href=&quot;https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4887799883825181&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;width: 1rem;height: 1rem&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;央视新闻的微博视频&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br clear=&quot;both&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;clear: both&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;video controls=&quot;controls&quot; poster=&quot;https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hcqt6qukp2j61gn0tm1kx02.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 100%&quot;&gt;&lt;source src=&quot;https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/UVvWgMIwlx084tI9qOEo01041200C1Cp0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;amp;ori=0&amp;amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;amp;Expires=1724574908&amp;amp;ssig=CSMFT6enKO&amp;amp;KID=unistore,video&quot;&gt;&lt;source src=&quot;https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/NTbnBuWXlx084tI7VuZa01041200iU2M0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;amp;ori=0&amp;amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;amp;Expires=1724574908&amp;amp;ssig=2OLt1KWLbw&amp;amp;KID=unistore,video&quot;&gt;&lt;source src=&quot;https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/M9Ir0zPklx084tI7Q5mg01041200bQZA0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;amp;ori=0&amp;amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;amp;Expires=1724574908&amp;amp;ssig=8cnZSnRUTl&amp;amp;KID=unistore,video&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;视频无法显示，请前往&lt;a href=&quot;https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4887799883825181&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;微博视频&lt;/a&gt;观看。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/video&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/OtD70k6FT</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/OtD70k6FT</guid><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 11:39:10 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author><category>小卫唠健康</category></item><item><title>[单身狗]只吃素不吃肉，能减肥吗？很难！而且，不吃肉，你身体里的优质蛋白质等营养素含量太低，就容易出现缺铁性贫血、维生素B12缺乏等问题。[话筒]控制食物总...</title><description>&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[单身狗]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/co_niuec-7d05bc992a.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;只吃素不吃肉，能减肥吗？&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;很难！而且，不吃肉，你身体里的优质蛋白质等营养素含量太低，就容易出现缺铁性贫血、维生素B12缺乏等问题。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[话筒]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;控制食物总能量才是关键，而不是只追求荤或素。宝，听进去了吗？&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%E9%97%AE%E7%AD%94%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%E9%97%AE%E7%AD%94%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫辟谣问答#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（健康中国） &lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hsxza9bucij20u018gdlx.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/OtCAflJZi</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/OtCAflJZi</guid><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 10:18:28 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author><category>小卫辟谣问答</category></item><item><title>🥚一颗鸡蛋，是蛋白的营养高，还是蛋黄的营养高？鸡蛋的主要营养，都在蛋黄里[doge]蛋白是优质的低脂高蛋白质食材，可蛋黄比它更优秀！不仅同样有优质蛋白质，...</title><description>🥚一颗鸡蛋，是蛋白的营养高，还是蛋黄的营养高？&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;鸡蛋的主要营养，都在蛋黄里&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[doge]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;蛋白是优质的低脂高蛋白质食材，可蛋黄比它更优秀！不仅同样有优质蛋白质，它的钙、锌、VA、VB1、VB2、卵磷脂等营养素，能甩蛋白几条街！&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%E9%97%AE%E7%AD%94%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%E9%97%AE%E7%AD%94%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫辟谣问答#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（广东疾控）&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;可它为什么这么噎......&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[二哈]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hsxx12u3l9j20k00gkmy9.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hsxx12vgmlj20ri0zrdkq.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hsxx12wa94j209208rq3a.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/OtC4Aac1i</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/OtC4Aac1i</guid><pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 09:00:26 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫